# GamifiedLearner backend needs NO secrets of its own.
#
# API keys belong to the LEARNER, not the server: the browser encrypts the
# user's key in IndexedDB and sends it per-request. The backend is a stateless
# proxy and never stores a key. This file exists only to document that there is
# nothing to configure — the app runs with an empty environment.
#
# Optional overrides:
# GL_CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173   # (not currently read; CORS origins are set in app/main.py)
